These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, september, july
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hedgehog##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | july | june     | september | april |
| Pet     | bird     | hedgehog | rabbit  | fish      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
House: cottage, cape-cod, victorian, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, old-henry, swisher, alhambra
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the victorian house is on the far right##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| House   | cottage | cape-cod    | farmhouse     | victorian  |
| Cigar     | dannemann    | swisher | old-henry | alhambra |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, roller, bike, jet-ski
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Transport   | roller   | bike   | taxi  | jet-ski |
| Beverage           | water | mirinda | iced-tea | soy-milk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, canasta, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, 7up, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing backgammon and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | snooker | backgammon | scrabble | canasta  |
| Beverage   | sprite  | cola   | iced-tea  | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
House: cape-cod, wooden, modern, farmhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, quad-bike, ship
1. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the wooden house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person driving the ship is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| House   | cape-cod    | wooden   | modern | farmhouse    |
| Transport      | roller | van | quad-bike       | ship |

