.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, firefighter, fisherman, lawyer
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, drawing, video-games, traveling
1. the lawyer is on the right of the fisherman##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the fisherman##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the teacher##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
5. the firefighter is on the left or right of the lawyer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Job    | teacher | fisherman | lawyer | firefighter |
| Hobby   | drawing | puzzles  | video-games    | traveling  |

