.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
House: modern, townhouse, tower, gothic-revival
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, poppy, rose
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the tower house is between the townhouse house and the gothic-revival house##2
5. the person who growsdaisy is the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growspoppy and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival | tower | townhouse     |
| Flower     | lily | rose  | daisy   | poppy |

