.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, car, scooter
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, thai, russian
1. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the colombian##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the thai##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the colombian is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Transport         | scooter | car | van | helicopter   |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai | japanese      | russian |

