.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, tiparillo, dannemann
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, bird, rabbit
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the rat##2
3. the havana-smoker is the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | havana | tiparillo      | dannemann   |
| Pet   | bird  | rat    | snake | rabbit |

