.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, bongani, oliveros
There 4 different types of food: lime, zucchini, cauliflower, cherry
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating cherry is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar       | blend | bongani | oliveros    | old-henry      |
| Food   | cauliflower       | cherry       | zucchini | lime |

