.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer, basketball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Sport   | cycling     | snowboarding  | basketball | soccer |
| Birthday     | september | june | january     | july    |

