.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, baccarat, fonseca, montecristo
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, 7up, milk
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the blend-smoker is the blend-smoker##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | blend | fonseca  | montecristo | baccarat |
| Beverage           | 7up     | milk | juice    | iced-tea     |

