.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
City: hannover, nizza, berlin, boston
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, boat, bike, jet-ski
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| City   | nizza  | hannover | boston  | berlin      |
| Transport    | jet-ski | ship | bike | boat |

