.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, apricot, lemon, lime
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, snake, rat
1. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person eating apricot is the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating lemon##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
6. the owner of the snake is the person eating peach##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Food         | apricot | lime | lemon | peach |
| Pet   | rat     | mouse       | hedgehog   | snake      |

