.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, cat, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, drawing, baking, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | turtle | cat | snake |
| Hobby         | drawing  | baking   | video-games | singing     |

