.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, lavender, mauve, amber
City: prague, edinburgh, liverpool, new-york
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Color      | emerald | lavender    | amber  | mauve |
| City   | prague       | edinburgh | liverpool | new-york  |

