3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the doctor##3
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the freelancer is between the person driving the skateboard and the manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Transport   | bike | boat  | snowmobile  | skateboard |
| Job           | doctor    | manager | freelancer | software-developer |

