.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, bartender, social-worker, photographer
4 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, rat, cat
1. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the cat is the owner of the cat##1
3. the photographer is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the manager##1
7. the social-worker is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Job   | bartender     | manager     | social-worker          | photographer |
| Pet      | ferret | horse | cat | rat  |

 